# Changelog for abbr.py

## [Unreleased]

## [0.1.2.1] 2020-11-19
### Changed
- Changed hotstring parsing regex to use * instead of + for replacement
- Changed default hotstring filename from 'hotstrings.txt' to 'hotstrings.ahk'

## [0.1.2] 2020-05-19
### Added
- Add support for 'C0', '*' options

## [0.1.1] 2019-10-12
### Added
- Add support for specifying hotstring filename
- Add support for directional keys
- Add support for 'O', 'B0' options

## [0.1.0] 2019-09-25
### Added
- Initial release
- Added support for comments